==Spanish==
==={{initialism}}===
[[Category:Internet laughter slang]]
'''ROFLMAO'''

#(''Internet'') rolling on the floor laughing my ass (arse) off, an extended form of [[ROFL]] formed by the combining with [[LMAO]]; used to indicate great amusement at something read on in a discussion group, ''etc''.

The word [[ROFLMAO]] can be said outloud, pronounced "roffle-maw", like the "m" in "mother" and the "aw" as-in "OW get off my foot". The pronunciation "roffle-MAY-oh" is also common.
It is usually said outloud by London kids, so don't try it if you live in [[Bolton]].

